

	 
      I miss you... Like the flower in the Winter missing the Spring.   I miss you... Like the wave in the ocean missing the shore.  I miss you... Like the seedling in the dark forest missing the light.  I miss you... Like the stream on the mountain missing the rain.  I miss you... I cried.  And Spring came...and the wave tumbled... And the seedling grew... and it rained.  And it came to be... this poem Somehow, made its way - to you... 
     
    
